node.text: It Is WhatEver U Want It To Be 🤍 @shopsaylav Swim Suit or Shirt Silly! 🤍  I’m being Flooded with Question and i D Love To Share …. Let me Say This Not that I Have To Explain, But I was in a car accident Drug by my hair A Block 1/2 by my hair when I was 7 the right side of my hip bone snapped and punctured my fallopian tube was damaged …. (Amongst So Many Other Things That Caused Me To Be In The Hospital for 1 Year) I’ve also had a tummy tuck after having my fourth baby who was almost 11 pounds they took off 2 1/2 Liters of skin and I’ve also had an emergency C-section with my third child so there you go!! And This Is Now What I’m Working With!!! But let’s be clear no matter what or whatever is happening to my body I have to work out @voltageindoorcycling \ @futureelite.academy @coachcait_h train and do the work no matter what I’ve done or the baby scars that I have I have to work out. PURRRRRRR LOL
